{"tid":1244481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】指速龍小隊2016年制服有編號 民權觀察：警方回應實屬荒謬","createTime":"2019-06-20T02:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T02:33:02.000Z","uid":56881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9070d80b65157936b48c6cd62e13fdba42242b88","tid":1244481,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T02:30:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%8C%87%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A2016%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F-%E6%B0%91%E6%AC%8A%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%AF%A6%E5%B1%AC%E8%8D%92%E8%AC%AC-130300583.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%259A%258A2016%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%25B6%25E6%259C%258D%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%2599%259F-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25AF%259F-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E8%258D%2592%25E8%25AC%25AC-130300583.html&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=b1d7e7cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%8C%87%E9%80%9F%E9%BE%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A2016%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F-%E6%B0%91%E6%AC%8A%E8%A7%80%E5%AF%9F-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%AF%A6%E5%B1%AC%E8%8D%92%E8%AC%AC-130300583.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oqES7gcLnP0_ReXnEWmX.Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190619a210510.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FoqES7gcLnP0_ReXnEWmX.Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190619a210510.jpg&h=910782e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在2016年的速龍小隊制服中，肩膊上有警員編號。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】金鐘立法會外上周三爆發警民衝突，導致多人受傷，保安局局長李家超表示，特別的工作服按照工作需要設計，在「速龍小隊」的制服上沒有位置展示警員編號，但指日後將作檢視，亦會有適當跟進。然而，民權觀察指，特別戰術小隊在2016年執勤時制服上仍有展示警員編號。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察表示，特別戰術小隊在2016年執勤時，其制服上仍有展示警員編號，質疑新制服無展示警員編號的設計是蓄意阻礙市民辨識警員身份，協助警員逃避在濫權或使用過量武力時的法律責任。<span style=\"color: red;\">民權觀察亦指，特別戰術小隊的頭盔印有「警察POLICE」的字樣、警員的戰術背心亦有位置展示警員編號，認為警方指新制服「無位置展示警員編號」的回應實屬荒謬，並侮辱市民智慧。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，民權觀察又指，辨識警員身份是一切投訴警察的調查、問責行動的基礎，並指警方在安排特別戰術小隊執勤時，必須確保特別戰術小隊的警員在頭盔及制服上清楚展示警員編號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁咩人著左套衫都唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a17111f86efea4c0aeddaea3a72046953dd21cd","tid":1244481,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"推"}]}